@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ectdsp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.abs(wp.cos(v0 + 0.28)))
    v0 = wp.sin(((v2 + 0.12 / v2 + 0.61) - wp.exp(v0 + 0.01)))
    v0 = (v1 * (wp.abs(tmp + 0.07) * (v0 + 0.86 / v2 + 0.50)))
    v2 = wp.sin(((v0 + 0.45 - tmp + 0.16) - (v2 + 0.56 / v2 + 0.24)))
    data[tid] = v0
